"{\"uid\": \"citizen.co.za-lifestyle-paris-2024-olympics-spreading-love-with-condoms-but-no-champagne\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home\\u00bbLifestyle Compiled byCarien Grobler Deputy Digital Editor 3 minute read 4 June 2024 05:43 pm In the romantic city of Paris, where pandemic-era Olympic restrictions have eased, the 2024 Games are fostering connections among athletes once more.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 128, \"end\": 133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999943061084, \"rank\": 5.693834775662222e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Home\\u00bbLifestyle Compiled byCarien Grobler Deputy Digital Editor\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 62}, {\"ngram\": \"the romantic city\", \"from\": 101, \"to\": 118}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 127}, {\"ngram\": \"pandemic-era Olympic restrictions\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 168}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Games\", \"from\": 181, \"to\": 195}, {\"ngram\": \"connections\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 221}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Approximately 300 000 condoms will be provided in the Olympic Village - nearly two per athlete for each day of the event.\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 308, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5358869573523506e-16, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Approximately 300 000 condoms\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 348}, {\"ngram\": \"each day\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 361}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After receiving the keys,Sky Newsaccompanied Games officials on inspections of the Olympic Village, which will host 9 000 athletes in July.\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 460, \"end\": 475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5358869573523506e-16, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the keys\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 401}, {\"ngram\": \"inspections\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 452}, {\"ngram\": \"9 000 athletes\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the tour, they discovered an unexpected feature: the bed frames are made of sturdy cardboard, capable of supporting up to 250kg of Olympian weight.\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 656, \"end\": 664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999997427987968, \"rank\": 2.2519854836470767e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tour\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"an unexpected feature\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 572}, {\"ngram\": \"the bed frames\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"sturdy cardboard\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 617}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 250kg\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dubbed \\\"anti-sex\\\" beds by organisers of the 2021 Tokyo Games, the cardboard-beds installed at the Olympic Village in Paris ahead of the 2024 games have generated quite a buzz.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999943061084, \"rank\": 5.693834775662222e-0